==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cowan
<hw>Cow"an</hw> <pr>(kou"⟦ait⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>couillon</ets> a coward, a cullion.]</ety> <def>One who works as a
mason without having served a regular apprenticeship.</def>
<mark>[Scot.]</mark> <note>Among Freemasons, it is a cant term for
<xex>pretender</xex>, <xex>interloper</xex>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coward</ent>⟦br⟧
